## ğŸ“Š Gender Stereotypes Analysis (R)

### ğŸ“ Overview
This project explores **gender stereotypes** using data from the international  
**Towards Gender Harmony** study.  
The analysis focuses on how **sensitivity** and **competitiveness** are perceived in women and men across different demographic and cultural contexts.

The results are presented as an **R Markdown HTML report**.

