### ğŸ“‚ Data
- **Source:** Towards Gender Harmony (open-access)
- **Observations:** 33,313
- **Countries:** 62
- **Years:** 2018â€“2020  
- **Dataset:** https://osf.io/trkyc/files/w6bt3

